task 3 -
CODE -
         a = input("enter string:")
         lens = len(a)%2 
         middleletter = a[lens]
         convertingmiddleletter = middleletter.upper()
         print(a.replace(middleletter,convertingmiddleletter))
OUTPUT -
         enter string:hello
         hEllo

